market_context: FOMC minutes confirm patient approach to rate cuts. Labor market remains resilient with jobless claims below 220K. S&P 500 hovering near all-time highs with mixed sector performance.

predictions.reasoning: Strong labor market data provides floor for equities. FOMC patience removes rate cut uncertainty as a negative catalyst. Historically, markets rally on 'good news is good news' when inflation is controlled.
Meta's AI infrastructure investment story resonating with investors. Reels engagement metrics tracking above expectations per third-party data. Ad revenue recovering in key verticals.
Tesla faces ongoing demand concerns in Europe and China. Recent delivery data disappoints. Musk distraction premium has turned into a discount as political controversy weighs on brand perception.
Dow industrials supported by strong employment backdrop. Financial and healthcare components showing relative strength. Pullback from highs represents buying opportunity for value-oriented positions.
